    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Knives, the blade of which is usually curved on one side and straight on the other, used to apply and smooth plaster.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
